+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+     install instructions for projects                   +
+                              projecthours               +
+                              projectstatistics          + 
+                              projectbilling             +
+                              projectdelivery            +          
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+       first edit the inc/phpgwapi/phpgw.inc.php        +
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
  add to class phpgw:
        
        var $dbtemp;


  add to function phpgw: 

  $this->dbtemp           = new db;
  $this->dbtemp->Host     = $phpgw_info["server"]["db_host"];                           
  $this->dbtemp->type     = $phpgw_info["server"]["db_type"]; 
  $this->dbtemp->Database = $phpgw_info["server"]["db_name"];  
  $this->dbtemp->User     = $phpgw_info["server"]["db_user"];   
  $this->dbtemp->Password = $phpgw_info["server"]["db_pass"];                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                   
    if ($this->debug) {                                                                                                                          
        $this->dbtemp->Debug = 1;                                                                                                                
            }

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+                install the datebase                      +
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

create_tables.mysql [ can be found in projects-directory ]

lang.sql [ can be found in each project*-directory ]


++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+                    project Admin                         +
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

create a group projectAdmin
each member of this group is able to edit or delete all created 
projects

also the chosen coordinator of a project is able to manage his
project 


the projects-app is required for running the other apps.
it needs at least projects and projecthours to manage jobs.
projectbilling is needed to create invoices.
projectstatistics creates user- and projectstats.
projectdelivery manages delivery notes. 

  